    "title": "Lead Frontend Developer at Infosys Advisory Limited",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Frontend Developer with drive and ambition, Infosys Advisory Limited in Navi Mumbai is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Infosys Advisory Limited:\nInfosys Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in Java\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Navi Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Infosys Advisory Limited!",
